{"tid":757201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港真係好撚多刁民，做CS慘過食屎","createTime":"2018-07-26T15:28:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T15:49:11.000Z","uid":194412,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1f188f730e530dd75ef5d0b4c0868ab9aad1097a","tid":757201,"uid":194412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:28:23.000Z","msg":"如題。<br />\n全部活動報撚哂，overlap都照報，我唔信你識分身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n係人都知唔同活動係唔同人負責，你問啲嘢我答你唔到係我錯嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，資料寫唔齊問返你係我錯嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。報名表填唔齊嘢其實根本就唔撚應該俾你報啦，好心問返你幫你填返又俾你屌，你想點撚樣呀 。填張表都隊俾CS填你文盲呀，咁怕麻煩咪唔好撚報囉，個活動唔洗錢㗎，serve到你咁仲想點呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n等兩分鐘就話要搵CEO傾，on99人哋秒秒鐘幾十萬上落好心你唔好阻撚住哂個地球轉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。再講人哋都未撚睇過份報名表呀，你想人哋點答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？一話你知人哋都答你唔到不如叫返負責開個同事覆就開波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，「你有咩資格講佢答我唔到？你係佢包嘅二奶？」屌依句真係難撚聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，你有呀媽生我有呀媽生，調返轉頭我鬧你係雞吖，你呀媽又有咩感想呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n奉勸各位下年諗住Intern做CS嘅巴絲諗清楚，香港真係好撚多刁民 。<br />\nP.S. 條臭西冇鄉音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b192d08417aa48d8a97c4aabbb1775ce88ef82fd","tid":757201,"uid":128441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:29:45.000Z","msg":"到你收工咪你畀屎人食囉"},{"pid":"9b7b838b10200d07aa879c66d726360f3ca34c8a","tid":757201,"uid":85416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T15:30:29.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母咁撚賤<br />\n賤到咁既嘢佢都諗到嚟講真係好嘢"},{"pid":"0bfdc8c98d379ecb8edf40cabd65542489d0bbeb","tid":757201,"uid":194412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9b7b838b10200d07aa879c66d726360f3ca34c8a","tid":757201,"uid":85416,"like":0,"di